data.description:
Discover your dream home in Green Valley, Henderson, NV. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem offers a perfect blend of comfort and luxury.

Upon entry, you'll be greeted by The spacious living room is ideal for relaxation and entertaining. The kitchen is complete with stainless steel appliances, solar water heater, brand new ac, new windows.

The master suite includes an en-suite bathroom for added convenience.

The real treasure of this property is the backyard. You'll find a sparkling pool and a luxurious jacuzzi, perfect for unwinding or hosting gatherings with friends and family.

Located in the heart of Green Valley, you'll have easy access to top-notch schools, shopping, dining, and scenic parks. The Las Vegas Strip is just a short drive away, offering world-class entertainment.

Don't miss this chance to call this Green Valley property your own. Schedule a showing today and start living your dream life in this oasis of comfort and style.
